---
const year = new Date().getFullYear();
---

<footer class="mt-auto border-t border-white/[0.06] bg-paper-warm/80 backdrop-blur-sm">
  <div class="page-container py-14">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-12 gap-10 md:gap-8">
      <div class="md:col-span-5">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-5">
          <img src="/favicon.svg" alt="" class="w-8 h-8" width="32" height="32" />
          <span class="font-display text-xl font-bold text-ink">Truffe<span class="text-alert">.</span>info</span>
        </div>
        <p class="text-sm text-ink-muted leading-relaxed max-w-sm">
          Progetto open source dedicato alla raccolta e diffusione di informazioni
          sulle truffe in Italia. Ogni segnalazione, anche di un tentativo non riuscito,
          contribuisce a proteggere gli altri.
        </p>
        <div class="flex gap-3 mt-6">
          <span class="tag">Open source</span>
          <span class="tag">MIT</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="md:col-span-3 md:col-start-7">
        <h3 class="section-label mb-4">Navigazione</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-2.5 text-sm text-ink-muted">
          <li><a href="/truffe" class="hover:text-trust transition-colors">Tipi di truffa</a></li>
          <li><a href="/segnala" class="hover:text-trust transition-colors">Segnala una truffa</a></li>
          <li><a href="/storie" class="hover:text-trust transition-colors">Storie di truffa</a></li>
          <li><a href="/chi-siamo" class="hover:text-trust transition-colors">Chi siamo</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="md:col-span-3">
        <h3 class="section-label mb-4">Legale</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-2.5 text-sm text-ink-muted">
          <li><a href="/linee-guida" class="hover:text-trust transition-colors">Linee guida</a></li>
          <li><a href="/segnala-contenuto" class="hover:text-trust transition-colors">Segnala un contenuto</a></li>
          <li><a href="/privacy" class="hover:text-trust transition-colors">Privacy</a></li>
          <li><a href="/termini" class="hover:text-trust transition-colors">Termini</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="border-t border-white/[0.06] mt-12 pt-6 flex flex-col sm:flex-row justify-between items-center gap-4 text-xs text-ink-faint">
      <p>&copy; {year} Truffe.info</p>
      <p>Protezione collettiva contro le truffe online</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
